  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study investigates the impact of the implementation of a surgical checklist on the
      mortality 30 days and 90 days after surgery. Patients scheduled for elective surgical
      procedures (excluding cardiac surgery) lasting at least 15 minutes are eligible. Surgery is
      performed in a single tertiary care center. The study is an open trial before and after
      intervention (implementation of the checklist &quot;safe surgery saves lifes&quot;).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
